original_title: Manhattan: Terrace View Avenue - Teunissen Place
text:
Terrace View Ave., (foreground) west side, at Teunissen Place (automobile thereon) and viewing northwestward across the valley housing the New York Central Railroad Freight Yards, to Spuytin Duyvil Hill; a portion of the Bronx.

October 26, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
